item.title: The Fastest Way to Lose Weight is Amputation but Don't Do That
item.description:
This video is just to address a very common question I get.
It's not meant to anger anyone or try to be clickbait. It's just to try to encourage people to think about their long-term results and not focus on sacrificing health for speed.
By the way, if "eat less" is not working for you, my favorite way to lose FAT is to just put on some extra muscle. Growing the large muscles of the body with squats, deadlifts, and pullups really increases the energy demands of the body, which can put you in a caloric deficit even if your diet remains the same. I've found it can make a big difference.
Legal Notice: Consult your doctor before beginning any kind of exercise program. This video does not replace a physical therapy program or consultation with a medical professional.
#shorts #hybridcalisthenics #weightloss

item.title: The World's Only Airport Where The Runway Is A Beach
item.description:
Barra Airport, in Na h-Eileanan Siar in the west of Scotland, is unique: it's the only commercial airport where the runway's made of sand, and tide covers it up twice a day. Here's how it works.
Thanks to all the team at Barra Airport: https://www.hial.co.uk/barra-airport
I chartered with Hebridean Air Services from Oban: https://www.hebrideanair.co.uk/
Scheduled flights are available with Loganair: https://www.loganair.co.uk/
Editor: Michelle Martin (@mrsmmartin) Location fixer: Vikki McCraw from Locations 365 http://locations365.co.uk
Filmed safely: https://www.tomscott.com/safe/
